<html><head /><body># Project PRD: Ayurveda – Ancient Wisdom, Modern Precision

## 1. Project Overview
Ayurveda is a high-end e-commerce platform and administrative ecosystem for a premium botanical apothecary. The brand, **Botanical Heritage**, bridges traditional Ayurvedic formulations with a modern, clinical aesthetic.

## 2. Brand Identity &amp; Design System
*   **Name:** Botanical Heritage
*   **Design Philosophy:** Editorial, serene, and professional. High-contrast typography paired with generous whitespace and botanical imagery.
*   **Typography:**
    *   **Headlines:** Noto Serif (reflecting tradition and heritage).
    *   **Body/Utility:** Manrope or sans-serif equivalent (reflecting modern precision).
*   **Color Palette:**
    *   **Primary:** Deep Forest Green (#1b4332)
    *   **Surface:** Off-white/Cream (#f8f9fa)
    *   **Accent:** Soft Sage and muted earth tones.
*   **Visual Elements:** Glassmorphism in navigation, card-based layouts for data, and high-fidelity studio photography of products and herbs.

## 3. User Experience (Storefront)
### 3.1 Authentication &amp; Onboarding
*   **Login:** Split-pane layout with brand imagery.
*   **Create Account:** Modern form with clear validation and botanical context.
*   **Forgot Password:** Minimalist recovery flow.

### 3.2 Product Discovery
*   **Home Page:** Long-form scrolling experience with hero banners, "Explore by Concern" categories, and featured products.
*   **Product Gallery:** Grid-based layout with a robust filtering sidebar (Category, Price Range, Wellness Type).
*   **Product Detail:** High-detail view with multi-image support and in-depth description.

### 3.3 Commerce Flow
*   **Shopping Cart:** Single-page summary with item management, subtotal calculations, and a clear "Buy Now" path.
*   **User Profile:** Centralized hub for managing personal information, security settings, and order history.
*   **Notifications:** System and order status updates for the user.

## 4. Administrative Ecosystem (Admin Portal)
### 4.1 Management Dashboard
*   KPI widgets for Revenue, Active Users, Total Orders, and Customer Satisfaction.
*   Real-time activity feeds for Recent Orders and Feedback.

### 4.2 Content &amp; Marketing Management
*   **Marketing Settings:** Field-level control for the "Header Message" (promotional bar) and Homepage Hero Banners.
*   **Hero Editor:** Support for updating headline text, subheadlines, CTA buttons, and banner images.

### 4.3 Inventory &amp; Product Management
*   **Add Product:** Multi-step form supporting up to 5 product images, SKU, Price, and Description.
*   **Inventory List:** Searchable table with status toggles (Active/Draft) and a secure deletion flow with confirmation dialogs.

### 4.4 User &amp; Order Oversight
*   **User Management:** Complete searchable user list with the ability to assign/revoke administrative privileges.
*   **Feedback Management:** Aggregated customer reviews and satisfaction metrics.
*   **Order Management:** Comprehensive order tracking with filtering by status (Processing, Shipped, Delivered, Cancelled).

## 5. Technical Requirements (Based on Backend API)
*   **Product Management:** CRUD operations for botanical items.
*   **Order System:** Real-time state management for customer orders.
*   **Role-Based Access:** Secure differentiation between Customer and Admin permissions.
*   **Marketing API:** Dynamic fetching of header messages and banner content for the storefront.

## 6. Success Metrics
*   Consistent visual identity across all 20+ generated screens.
*   Seamless transition between user-facing storefront and administrative backend.
*   Mobile-responsive parity for all core shopping and management flows.</body></html>